txt.en: Mount your steed and talk to Rahâzi at TBD to undertake the urgent mission
Talk to Khashig at his guard-post east of Umbar Baharbêl
The Song of Waves and Wind must not be permitted to endanger the lands of Middle-earth.
Chapter 18.1: Outrun the Wind, Outrun the Waves
Rahâzi is at TBD with an urgent mission for you.
Khashig stands at his guard-post east of Umbar Baharbêl.
